.gsdesearch\ARCHITECTURE.md:13:For Android-first polish and later expansion, add a dedicated mobile platform layer around the existing web app. That layer should own app lifecycle, safe-area and system UI behavior, haptics, splash/loading readiness, back-button policy, packaging, and release automation. The engine should remain portable and unaware of Capacitor or Android specifics.
